divs: sighting detailsi was on the boardwalk at "the sands"(a beach) in port royal,sc taking pictures of dolphins and the sunset. i didn't see nor did i hear anything. it was only after i downloaded the photos that i noticed the strange object at the top of the photo. though the photo is blurry, when zoomed in the object seems to have what appears to be similar lights on each side(?), however, i leave it to the experts to decide\figure out what it might be(if anything) thanks you
